als or plants. What is organic? Why is that important? What is the outcoming?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They prefer organic... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) organic farming techniques<br />\n\t2) organic compounds<br />\n\t3) organic food market<br />\n\t4) promote the importance of organic<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tSeeing the line up of people today gave him an idea, perhaps he should consider adding gourmet pizza to the menu at his restaurant. Maybe he could even use that as the main selling point in the take-out menu. Often, it was not difficult to make a regular dish into a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/gourmet\" target=\"_blank\">gourmet</a> dish. All that was needed was to switch up the ingredients, for instance, instead of the basic mushroom, he could use portabella mushrooms. As for the cheese, it could definitely be upgraded. He could also use organic vegetables, sourcing from local farmers.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/167864961361/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p788004/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p788004\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p796132/\">陈妍希陈晓今日大婚！过儿熬成了姑父！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p794776/\">男人最看重女人什么？并不仅仅是肤白貌美哦</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p795993/\">意大利最后一位王子在街头卖意面……WHAT？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p79598